text: HDFC is great probably they have many good people to work for them. It was before core banking and there were no core banking, and not many ATMs. I wanted some money and at a branch in Andheri W, I tried to withdraw money outside a branch. ATM was not working. I approached the BM and he asked how much I needed. I said 3000, I got one withdrawal slip or something filled and gave me the money. I took the money and asked him how he gave the money without my signature record. He said he has some amount limit which could be written off in case I was a fraud. But if I was genuine, he said he was sure I would be speaking highly of his bank to hundreds of people. You can well how many years, and I still remember the manager‚Äôs deeds, though nothing of his name. Hope he is healthy at whatever age he is at.
